#. Tag: title
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a bond"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: textobject
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Cockpit adding bond</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When adding a bonding interface, enter a name and specify which interfaces "
"to include. If possible, proceed with other items as suggested by Cockpit. "
"However, you can select one of the following modes:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Round Robin"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Transfers packets from the first available interface to the last. The mode "
"offers fault tolerance and load balancing."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Active Backup"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only one interface in the bonding is active. If the active interface fails, "
"the backup will be activated."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balance XOR"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Balancing using a transmit hash policy. The default is a modulo device "
"count. To select a different policy, specify the <literal>xmit_hash_policy</"
"literal> option in the <guimenu>Option</guimenu> field."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "Broadcast"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Evrything is transmitted on all interfaces."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "802.3ad Dynamic Link Aggregation"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates aggregation groups that share the same speed and duplex settings."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adaptive Transmit Load Balancing"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Is a channel bonding that does not require any special switch support. The "
"outgoing traffic is distributed according to the current load on each "
"interface."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adaptive Load Balancing"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Includes adaptive transmit load balancing and receive load balancing, no "
"special switch support is required."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also provide more options in the field <guimenu>Options</guimenu> "
"using the <emphasis>key=value</emphasis> format."
